<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ de dān zi shì qīng shěng de 迦南171</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ de dān zi shì qīng shěng de, zhǔ de è shì róng yì de.
 nǐ láo kǔ ma? nǐ chóu fán ma? kě yǐ dào shén miàn qián xiǎng ān xī.
 zhǔ de dān zi zhēn shì qīng shěng de, zhǔ de è zhēn shì róng yì de,
 nǐ láo kǔ ma? nǐ chóu fán ma? kě yǐ dào shén miàn qián xiǎng ān xī.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>171</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>